_sText:
This map depicts the Global Gamecast studio's in downtown Greenville SC.
The most notable DJ booth is suspended in the main atrium in the glass chamber on the 4th floor.
Visit http://www.globalgamecast.com and tune in for the show on Tuesdays & Fridays @11:00pm

There is a secret way to get to the upper offices during gameplay

Download and enjoy!!

Includes:
NAV MESH + RADAR in the BSP
